spyq-2-en.text: What's the biggest thrill you have ever had at work?

spyq-3-en.text: Sorry,  but who are you again?

spyq-4-en.text: What is the Pension Plan like with your job?

spyq-5-en.text: Do you think this place is dangerous?

spyq-6-en.text: How did you get here today?

spyq-7-en.text: How long did it take you to get here today?

spyq-8-en.text: What do you see out the window?

spyq-9-en.text: What's your favorite perk of the job?

spyq-10-en.text: What would it take for me to do your job?

spyq-13-en.text: Apart from me,  who was the last person you spoke to?

spyq-14-en.text: How was your ride to work this morning?

spyq-15-en.text: What time was your last break?

spyq-17-en.text: If I told you <insert name here> was the spy,  would you be surprised?

spyq-19-en.text: What's that in your other hand?

spyq-20-en.text: What was your last Christmas party like?

spyq-21-en.text: What did you eat for lunch today?

spyq-24-en.text: What is your biggest workday challenge?

spyq-25-en.text: What is the most satisfying part of your job?

spyq-26-en.text: What are the employee benefits of working here?

spyq-32-en.text: What does it say in the window?

spyq-33-en.text: What's the biggest problem with what you're wearing?

spyq-34-en.text: What magazines do you subscribe to?

spyq-35-en.text: If you are the spy,  what would your code name be?

spyq-36-en.text: What is your favorite piece of workplace furniture?

spyq-37-en.text: If I got covered in oil,  what would you think?

spyq-39-en.text: Who is your most irritating co-worker?

spyq-41-en.text: What Time Does Your Job End?

spyq-43-en.text: How Would You Describe The People Around You?

spyq-44-en.text: Sorry,  But Who Are You Again?

spyq-45-en.text: Why Did You Speak To The Last Person You Spoke To?

spyq-46-en.text: What's Your Favorite Type of Table?

spyq-47-en.text: What Tool Do You Use Most In Your Job?

spyq-48-en.text: Would you bring your family here?

spyq-50-en.text: Why would you recommend this place to a friend?
